me
what den? now you jes show your red pate round dat
treedat's allelse you stay dare till Mass Henrich come back and
den we hab you on bofe sides.
Harry, you fool! you idiot! you dolt! Harry, I say!
Golly, but he must
know
me! said Harryand den he talk
good English too, for an Indian.
Don't you know your friend Henrich Huntington? asked the
