'Course I do, answered the other, keeping equally close behind
his cover, and still unsuspicious of the true state of the casehe's
coming pretty soon, so you better s'render!
He's here, I tell you againI am Henrich myself!
You're a lying Injun! replied the other, indignantlyI know
